// Signing.local.xcconfig.example — committed template.
//
// Copy to Signing.local.xcconfig (gitignored) and set your team ID.
// Find it at https://developer.apple.com/account → Membership Details.
//
// A free Apple ID team ID also works; the project signs with the
// Apple Development identity on dev builds and ad-hoc (`-`) signature
// on the release DMG.

DOTZAP_DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_TEAM_ID
